      "message": "[error] Line 151: `info-\u003econtacts-\u003eload()` triggers `loadTrustRequests()`, which calls `onTrustRequest(..., confirm\u003dfalse, ...)` for every cached request, which unconditionally fires `callbacks_.trustRequest` (contact_list.cpp line 370). Similarly, `loadKnownDevices()` fires `callbacks_.devicesChanged`. Both callbacks fire here before `this_-\u003einfo_` is assigned at line 167, so any callback handler that dereferences account info will observe null or stale state. Consider deferring the `load()` call until after `this_-\u003einfo_` is fully populated, or suppress callback emission during the initial load (similar to how `updateContact(..., emit\u003dfalse)` is used in `loadContacts()`).",
